<measure quantity="6" unit="years">
<num value="6">六</num>年</measure>
<pc>，</pc>召見<pc>，</pc>賜緋<pc>，</pc>加<name key="王著" type="givenName">著</name>作佐郎<pc>、</pc>翰林侍書與侍讀<pc>，</pc>更直於禦書院<pc>。</pc>
